  <summary>&lt;p>MacOSX Mojave like circle icon theme for linux desktops&lt;br />--------------------------&lt;br />Based on OSX_ONE: &lt;a href="https://github.com/unc926/OSX_ONE">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://github.com/unc926/OSX_ONE">https://github.com/unc926/OSX_ONE&lt;/a>&lt;br />--------------------------&lt;br />&lt;b>You can use this with:&lt;/b>&lt;br />--------------------------&lt;br />&lt;b>GTK theme&lt;/b>&lt;br />Mojave-gtk-theme: &lt;a href="https://www.pling.com/p/1275087/">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://www.pling.com/p/1275087/">https://www.pling.com/p/1275087/&lt;/a>&lt;br />&lt;br />&lt;b>KDE theme&lt;/b>&lt;br />McMojave-kde: &lt;a href="https://www.pling.com/p/1304936/">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://www.pling.com/p/1304936/">https://www.pling.com/p/1304936/&lt;/a>&lt;br />&lt;br />&lt;b>Folder-color&lt;/b>&lt;br />Folder-color: &lt;a href="http://foldercolor.tuxfamily.org">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="http://foldercolor.tuxfamily.org">http://foldercolor.tuxfamily.org&lt;/a>&lt;br />--------------------------&lt;br />&lt;b>Info&lt;/b>&lt;br />--------------------------&lt;br />This theme use &lt;b>numix-icon-theme-circle&lt;/b> for Inherits&lt;br />so if you want a better experience you can install numix-circle&lt;br />&lt;br />&lt;b>numix-icon-theme-circle&lt;/b> :&lt;br />&lt;a href="https://github.com/numixproject/numix-icon-theme-circle">&lt;/a>&lt;a href="https://github.com/numixproject/numix-icon-theme-circle">https://github.com/numixproject/numix-icon-theme-circle&lt;/a>&lt;/p></summary>
